d only do so by 1 point?<br>
<br>
Example, random numbers out of my head.  Lets say a successful taunt give you 300 points of hate.  And Ranger d00d has built up 898 points of hate on our mob.  You start off with 0 hate.  You taunt successfully, mob turns to you momentarily, you are at 300 points of hate.  He still hates Ranger d00d more so turns back to him.  You taunt successfully a second time, mob turns to you momentarily again, you are 600 points of hate.  He still hates Ranger d00d more and turns back to him a second time.  You taunt successfully a third time, mob turns to you, you would theoretically have 900 points of hate, but because Ranger d00d only has 898 and is at the top of the hate list, you are placed at 899, one point above him.<br>
<br>
This SEEMS to be in line with what I frequently see happening.  No I can't prove it.  And no, I can't be sure its true.  But I do know that a successful taunt does not mean you get the undisputed attention of the mob.  Occassionally when trying to help a newbie out in EC or WC, I will walk up and taunt a mob, intending to gain its attention momentarily.  I have more than once taunted repeatedly and not been able to turn the mob.  Maybe all the taunts were failures, but that does seem to be quite a coincidence.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/uworrlorrd60.showPublicProfile?language=EN>worrlorrd60</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are Superior</span><br>  Posts: 6<br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/21/02 11:48:25 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1440.topic&index=14>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: address</span><hr size=1> Taunt is a myth... give it up =(  Its just a button that was put there to make us feel better, and feel like we are &quot;doing something&quot; during fights =/ <p><img src="http://home.bellsouth.net/coDataImages/bellsouthpwp/Groups/8/8336/pages/19228/WebSigwTitle.jpg" border="0"><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=109026"  target="_blank">Magelo Profile</a>
